{"tid":1632134,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「十年」學到最多的是陰謀論 失去最多的是信任","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T11:58:05.000Z","uid":7971,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d519c3a7bdd868642feb8bcdba2a39c6bb650d6c","tid":1632134,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/COOQdiy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOOQdiy.png&h=ef121959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連登係場運動 重要核心 </span></strong><br />\n點解？<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">因為連登發言 係不按身份 <br />\n<strong>可行就推 可行就做 </strong><br />\n唔會因爲你嘅社會地位 年齡 性別<br />\n你有道理就會上熱門</span><br />\n<br />\n但明顯愈黎愈多人<br />\n好容易就會話風向 陰謀論 五毛 <br />\n永遠唔岩聽 唔認同你意見<br />\n第一句 就屌人老母<br />\n第二句 就屌人冷氣撚<br />\n第三句 就屌人帶風向 陰謀論<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分區 vs 集中 嘅討論<br />\n裝修 嘅討論<br />\n私了 嘅討論<br />\n<br />\n總之好容易 有一班人 每一次都係屌咗先<br />\n然後覺得自己就係岩 自己就無錯<br />\n講唔到 駁唔到 <br />\n就會用上面「屌人三句」去合理化自己行為<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>都係個一句 前唔前線 投入咗幾多係場運動<br />\n無得fact check</strong></span><br />\n都唔好小學雞 講一句我前個你 就覺得好威威<br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>站穩自己立場下<br />\n不如睇多少少唔同光譜嘅論述</strong></span><br />\n(Eg 我由881商台嘅 血債票償論晴朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到陶傑 嘅小農DNA (精英主義)<br />\n到方志恆嘅 革新論<br />\n到陳雲 嘅中美自治論<br />\n到毓民 嘅 全民制憲<br />\n到鄭立、無侍堂 嘅本土述說<br />\n到堡主 嘅獨派述説)<br />\n<em>有錯請指正</em><br />\n<br />\n我都會睇 同 反思<br />\n只少我會好想知道<br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\">思考暫時仲係同一立場 <br />\n路上嘅其他人點諗 點去行依場運動</span><br />\n<br />\n如果真係唔認同對方立場，<br />\n但如果無好大影響，都唔係膠做<br />\n就真係採取各自爬山<br />\n但如果 最後你覺得係有影響到場運動，<br />\n你又唔同意<br />\n咁就據理力爭，<br />\n用你嘅言語、實際行動去感化其他人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係危難同亂世中，<br />\n我認為更重要 係時刻保持警覺同思考。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後唔好習慣，恆常化 <br />\n所有受傷 同 政權不合理嘅行為，<br />\n一定一定要提自己 唔好習慣。"},{"pid":"01b1dc6b78387cc3362ba2a1c3410d9adc7d71af","tid":1632134,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2c6ee4e4274fdec0a57cf12d0dfb5a3c8546b6d","tid":1632134,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2b5a70eea7810f6b145d9a75110f28217a3dc55","tid":1632134,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ca204c353946145eee0ba81a44ab7c1d49dd480","tid":1632134,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"750f757e802f31c9593715a1ebaca8317a092523","tid":1632134,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"913b07f6540b03c93ab177d3958c9d712af7662b","tid":1632134,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b44f3d7a808587a93c2fd9a9e198b0da71a29424","tid":1632134,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:11:02.000Z","msg":"可行的就推 可行的就做<br />\n但保持醒覺<br />\n<br />\n保持醒覺的方法 是冷靜發熱的頭腦<br />\n然後多讀 多睇不同光譜意見<br />\n用實際行動走出來<br />\n<br />\n可能阿媽係女人<br />\n但大家頭腦真係需要冷卻一下"},{"pid":"f19f44d20f14431e003ef1fe3380e048804f4ab5","tid":1632134,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:13:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8fb62e367fe4e7efd634c79aaa3ee13d2f41cb9","tid":1632134,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9fc6556227fe7019a2113403798d3669998923f","tid":1632134,"uid":187629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04280cee720be8d98889eb790a6d054aede9dfb7","tid":1632134,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:21:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c20841f1b030845ce232ffa2c51fdced868ab0d7","tid":1632134,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:33.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 10.7 爆食日 攪珠結果出爐<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632126</a>"},{"pid":"a9d0302875b065b1886c6383d905aae8855ec7a8","tid":1632134,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"014e4b300a2fd5b347ef160d610881e8c4b5840b","tid":1632134,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"655b7c782b1af82c8dae53f898fc867563db68d1","tid":1632134,"uid":246118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"從來依類引發思考嘅post都冇人覆<br />\n係大家咁啱睇唔到，定睇完就算，覆都懶得覆？"}]}